ActIndian Act
SubjectAddition to the Rainy River First Nations No. 2, Ontario
PrecisOrder setting apart 3,735.08 hectares (9,229.55 acres) of land including mines and minerals for the use and benefit of the Rainy River First Nations as an addition to RAINY RIVER FIRST NATIONS NO. 2, located within the municipal Township of Lake of the Woods and the municipal Township of Sioux Narrows – Nestor Falls and is approximately 12 kilometres from the village of Morson, in Ontario.
